{"article_id":"MvTzD7gml1cRchBm","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"'Words cant describe the loss , '","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"says father of victim","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"19 members of a `` hotshot '' team from Prescott died in the wildfire","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"The nearly 9,000-acre fire is the deadliest wildland blaze for firefighters in 80 years","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"They were part of an elite squad","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"confronting wildfires on the front line ,","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"setting up barriers","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"to stop the spreading destruction .","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"But in their unpredictable world , it does n't take much to turn a situation deadly .","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"In this case , a wind shift and other factors caused a central Arizona fire ,","depth":12},{"id":11,"text":"which now spans 8,400 acres ,","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"to become erratic ,","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"said Mike Reichling , Arizona State Forestry Division spokesman .","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"Though the deaths are under investigation ,","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"the inferno appears to have proved too much , even for the shelters","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"the 19 firefighters carried","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"as a last-ditch survival tool .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"`` The fuels were very dry ,","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"the relative humidity was low ,","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"the wind was coming out of the south .","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"It turned around on us","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"because of monsoon action , ''","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"Reichling told CNN affiliate KNXV .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"`` That 's what caused the deaths .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"The firefighters","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"-- members of the Prescott Fire Department 's Granite Mountain Hotshots --","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"were killed Sunday","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"while fighting the Yarnell Hill fire , northwest of Phoenix .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"Among the dead was Eric Marsh , the unit 's 43-year-old superintendent .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"'The fire just overtook them '","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"'The fire just overtook them '","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"02:48","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Remembering Hotshots firefighters","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"Remembering Hotshots firefighters","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"02:04","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"How do fire shelters work ?","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"How do fire shelters work ?","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"01:24","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"What is a Hotshot firefighter ?","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"What is a Hotshot firefighter ?","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"03:33","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"Also killed ,","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"according to the city of Prescott :","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"Andrew Ashcraft , 29 ; Robert Caldwell , 23 ; Travis Carter , 31 ; Dustin Deford , 24 ; Christopher MacKenzie , 30 ; Grant McKee , 21 ; Sean Misner , 26 ; Scott Norris , 28 ; Wade Parker , 22 ; John Percin , 24 ; Anthony Rose , 23 ; Jesse Steed , 36 ; Joe Thurston , 32 ; Travis Turbyfill , 27 ; William Warneke , 25 ; Clayton Whitted , 28 ; Kevin Woyjeck , 21 ; and Garret Zuppiger , 27 .","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"The deaths of the 19","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"-- representing about 20 percent of Prescott 's fire department --","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"devastated the city .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"Prescott Fire Chief Dan Fraijo ,","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"who sent the unit at the request of regional authorities ,","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"he was told that one of the firefighters had radioed","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"they were about to deploy their fire shelters , a sort of aluminum blanket","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"that protects against the flames and heat -- and a measure of last resort .","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"`` We just lost 19 of some of the finest people","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"you 'll ever meet .","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"Right now , we 're in crisis , ''","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"Fraijo told reporters .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"A 20th member of the unit was working on an assignment away from his team","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"and survived ,","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"Fraijo said .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"`` He feels terribly ,","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"and we all feel terribly .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"Unfortunately , we have very few words","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"to express that kind of sorrow ,","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"but we understood each other .","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"When you take a person in your arms","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"and you hug them ,","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"you do n't have to say too much , ''","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"A tribute to the firefighters grew Monday outside Prescott Fire Station No . 7 .","depth":5},{"id":83,"text":"Flowers , American flags and signs","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"-- including those","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"reading `` 19 Great guys gone","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"-- you will be missed ''","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"and `` Prescott 19 forever in our hearts '' --","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"were placed on or near a fence","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"that separated the station from a road .","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"The tokens also included 19 bottles of water ,","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"arranged in a circle .","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"Also left was a copy of The Firefighter 's Prayer ,","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"which contains the lines ,","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"`` And","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"if ,","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"according to my fate ,","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"I am to lose my life","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"/","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"Please bless with your protecting hand my children and my wife . ''","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"Gov . Jan Brewer called the loss `` unbearable '' during a Monday news conference","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"and said","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"she understood the pain","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"people are dealing with .","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"The wildfire ,","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"which is considered the deadliest in state history ,","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"began Friday near Yarnell ,","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"apparently because of lightning strikes ,","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"according to Brewer 's office and other authorities .","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"The fire was n't contained at all on Monday morning ,","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"and about 200 homes and other structures have burned in the area of Yarnell , a community of about 600 people ,","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"the state forestry division said .","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"About 400 ground personnel and 100 incident-management staff were working","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"to control the fire Monday .","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"There are no other reported injuries from the blaze ,","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"Reichling said .","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"`` As we face the day","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"the highest priority is for the fallen comrades , ''","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"said Roy Hall , an incident commander with the state forestry division .","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"`` We got a lot of hotshot crews in the nation ,","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"and they are the elite of the ground firefighters .","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"They 're highly trained and highly specialized .","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"They are a younger generation .","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"That 's the tragedy of it ,","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"that lives would be lost of such a young group . ''","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"He added of the fire ,","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"`` We know","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"that there are values","depth":15},{"id":128,"text":"to be protected","depth":15},{"id":129,"text":"and efforts","depth":15},{"id":130,"text":"that need to be ongoing in this fire .","depth":15},{"id":131,"text":"It 's a long ways from being over . ''","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"Firefighters will work on the eastern side of the fire in an effort","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"to protect homes in evacuated areas ,","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"as air tankers drop fire retardant on the perimeter","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"and five helicopters douse hot spots with water .","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"Billows of thick black smoke covered the sky","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"as the giant flames leaped from one stretch of parched land to another .","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"With high temperatures","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"-- it hit 98 degrees in Yarnell on Monday --","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"and dry fuel in the fire 's path , firefighters faced tough conditions in a race","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"to contain the blaze .","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"Sunday was the deadliest day for firefighters since the 9/11 attacks .","depth":7},{"id":143,"text":"And it is the deadliest wildland fire since 1933 ,","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"when 25 firefighters died","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"as a blaze burned in light chaparral near Griffith Park , California ,","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"according to a list from the U.S. National Wildfire Coordinating Group .","depth":8},{"id":147,"text":"Mary Rasmussen , spokeswoman for the incident command team","depth":7},{"id":148,"text":"charged with fighting the blaze ,","depth":7},{"id":149,"text":"said","depth":6},{"id":150,"text":"the cause of the firefighters ' deaths is being investigated ,","depth":6},{"id":151,"text":"and answers might come in the next three days .","depth":6},{"id":152,"text":"Authorities have information","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"that during the blaze , the firefighters deployed their fire shelters .","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"The shelters must be timed well .","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"Set it up too soon ,","depth":12},{"id":156,"text":"and the heat inside the shelter can become suffocating .","depth":12},{"id":157,"text":"Deploy it too late ,","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"and the fire is already on top of you .","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"Wearing gloves ,","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"a firefighter will lie on the ground under the shelter ,","depth":13},{"id":161,"text":"the ground being the only thing","depth":14},{"id":162,"text":"keeping the firefighter cool .","depth":14},{"id":163,"text":"The shelter will block 100 % of the heat from flames and hot gases and 95 % of the radiant heat from the flames themselves .","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"Drivers","depth":10},{"id":165,"text":"fleeing the area","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"were chased by dark plumes","depth":10},{"id":167,"text":"filling the air .","depth":10},{"id":168,"text":"Some evacuees paused","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"to look from afar ,","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"wondering","depth":10},{"id":171,"text":"if the flames had torched their homes .","depth":10},{"id":172,"text":"The blaze had n't touched Prescott yet .","depth":9},{"id":173,"text":"But like many other fire departments across the state , the Prescott team jumped in to help .","depth":9},{"id":174,"text":"`` A hotshot crew are the elite firefighters , ''","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"state forestry spokesman Art Morrison said .","depth":11},{"id":176,"text":"`` They 're usually ( a ) 20-person crew ,","depth":12},{"id":177,"text":"and they 're the ones","depth":13},{"id":178,"text":"who actually go in","depth":14},{"id":179,"text":"and dig the fire line ,","depth":15},{"id":180,"text":"cut the brush","depth":16},{"id":181,"text":"to make a fuel break .","depth":16},{"id":182,"text":"And so they would be as close to the fire","depth":12},{"id":183,"text":"as they felt","depth":13},{"id":184,"text":"they safely could . '' `","depth":13},{"id":185,"text":"` In normal circumstances ,","depth":12},{"id":186,"text":"when you 're digging fire line ,","depth":13},{"id":187,"text":"you make sure","depth":15},{"id":188,"text":"you have a good escape route ,","depth":15},{"id":189,"text":"and you have a safety zone set up , ''","depth":14},{"id":190,"text":"Morrison said .","depth":11},{"id":191,"text":"`` Evidently , their safety zone was n't big enough ,","depth":11},{"id":192,"text":"and the fire just overtook them . ''","depth":11},{"id":193,"text":"One of the firefighters","depth":11},{"id":194,"text":"-- Woyjeck , the son of a Los Angeles County fire captain --","depth":11},{"id":195,"text":"joined the Prescott unit just three months ago .","depth":10},{"id":196,"text":"Woyjeck , an avid outdoorsman , always wanted to be a firefighter like his father ,","depth":10},{"id":197,"text":"Joe Woyjeck told `` Anderson Cooper 360 '' on Monday evening .","depth":10},{"id":198,"text":"Joe Woyjeck said","depth":12},{"id":199,"text":"he last talked to his son by phone on Sunday morning .","depth":12},{"id":200,"text":"`` He said ,","depth":14},{"id":201,"text":"'Dad ,","depth":15},{"id":202,"text":"we got a fire in Yarnell , Arizona . ...","depth":15},{"id":203,"text":"I 'll give you a call later , ' ''","depth":13},{"id":204,"text":"the elder Woyjeck recalled .","depth":12},{"id":205,"text":"He said","depth":11},{"id":206,"text":"it has n't sunk in yet","depth":12},{"id":207,"text":"that he wo n't get that phone call .","depth":12},{"id":208,"text":"`` Words ca n't describe the loss","depth":11},{"id":209,"text":"that our family is feeling right now , ''","depth":11},{"id":210,"text":"Joe Woyjeck said .","depth":10},{"id":211,"text":"Kevin Woyjeck was n't the only firefighter 's son in the Granite Mountain crew .","depth":6},{"id":212,"text":"MacKenzie was the son of retired California Department of Forestry and Fire Protection Capt . Mike MacKenzie ,","depth":7},{"id":213,"text":"according to that department .","depth":7},{"id":214,"text":"Department of Homeland Security Secretary Janet Napolitano urged residents in the area to heed local authorities ' instructions ,","depth":6},{"id":215,"text":"while lamenting the loss of so many firefighters .","depth":6},{"id":216,"text":"`` Today , our thoughts and prayers go out to the families and loved ones of the 19 firefighters","depth":8},{"id":217,"text":"who lost their lives in the line of duty , ''","depth":8},{"id":218,"text":"she said in a written statement .","depth":7},{"id":219,"text":"`` As thousands of their colleagues continue to fight wildfires across Arizona and the West ,","depth":7},{"id":220,"text":"the Department of Homeland Security and FEMA are working closely with our federal partners","depth":9},{"id":221,"text":"including the Forest Service and the Department of Interior ,","depth":9},{"id":222,"text":"to support state and local efforts . ''","depth":8},{"id":223,"text":"President Barack Obama also lauded the efforts of the fallen firefighters ,","depth":7},{"id":224,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":225,"text":"their deaths are heartbreaking","depth":9},{"id":226,"text":"and `` our thoughts and prayers go out '' to their families .","depth":9},{"id":227,"text":"His administration stands ready to help in any way necessary ,","depth":7},{"id":228,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":229,"text":"`` They were heroes","depth":7},{"id":230,"text":"-- highly skilled professionals","depth":8},{"id":231,"text":"who ,","depth":10},{"id":232,"text":"like so many across our country do every day ,","depth":10},{"id":233,"text":"selflessly put themselves in harm 's way","depth":10},{"id":234,"text":"to protect the lives and property of fellow citizens","depth":11},{"id":235,"text":"they would never meet , ''","depth":11},{"id":236,"text":"he said in an earlier statement .","depth":6},{"id":237,"text":"Brewer ,","depth":11},{"id":238,"text":"who was to visit Prescott on Monday ,","depth":11},{"id":239,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":240,"text":"the loss marked `` as dark a day","depth":10},{"id":241,"text":"as I can remember . ''","depth":10},{"id":242,"text":"She has ordered","depth":10},{"id":243,"text":"state flags be flown at half-staff from sunrise Monday to sunset Wednesday ,","depth":10},{"id":244,"text":"and issued an emergency declaration","depth":10},{"id":245,"text":"that will make $ 200,000 available for response and recovery ,","depth":11},{"id":246,"text":"while authorizing mobilization of the National Guard ,","depth":12},{"id":247,"text":"if necessary .","depth":12},{"id":248,"text":"`` It may be days or longer","depth":11},{"id":249,"text":"before an investigation reveals","depth":12},{"id":250,"text":"how this tragedy occurred ,","depth":12},{"id":251,"text":"but the essence","depth":12},{"id":252,"text":"we already know in our hearts :","depth":12},{"id":253,"text":"fighting fires is dangerous work , ''","depth":11},{"id":254,"text":"she said .","depth":9},{"id":255,"text":"`` When a tragedy like this strikes ,","depth":9},{"id":256,"text":"all","depth":11},{"id":257,"text":"we can do","depth":11},{"id":258,"text":"is offer our eternal gratitude to the fallen , and prayers for the families and friends","depth":11},{"id":259,"text":"left behind . ''","depth":11},{"id":260,"text":"Fraijo said","depth":7},{"id":261,"text":"the firefighters","depth":10},{"id":262,"text":"who died","depth":10},{"id":263,"text":"were exceptionally dedicated to their jobs .","depth":9},{"id":264,"text":"`` These are the guys","depth":11},{"id":265,"text":"that will go out there with 40 , 50 pounds of equipment","depth":12},{"id":266,"text":"and walk five miles .","depth":12},{"id":267,"text":"They 'll sleep out there","depth":11},{"id":268,"text":"as they try to develop fire lines ''","depth":12},{"id":269,"text":"to protect homes ,","depth":12},{"id":270,"text":"Fraijo said .","depth":9},{"id":271,"text":"Before the 19 deaths in Arizona , 43 firefighters had been killed so far in 2013 ,","depth":7},{"id":272,"text":"according to the U.S. Fire Administration .","depth":7},{"id":273,"text":"A total of 83 firefighters died last year while on duty .","depth":6},{"id":274,"text":"`` Such a tragic loss , ''","depth":5},{"id":275,"text":"one person wrote .","depth":5},{"id":276,"text":"`` My heart aches for these brave souls , and for their families and friends . ''","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":553,"left":372,"right":552,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":372,"left":0,"right":371,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":371,"left":329,"right":370,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":329,"left":305,"right":328,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":305,"left":289,"right":304,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":289,"left":279,"right":288,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":279,"left":278,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":278,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":288,"left":4,"right":287,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":287,"left":282,"right":286,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":282,"left":280,"right":281,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":280,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":281,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":286,"left":9,"right":285,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":285,"left":284,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":284,"left":283,"right":12,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":283,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":304,"left":299,"right":303,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":299,"left":292,"right":298,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":292,"left":14,"right":291,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":291,"left":290,"right":17,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":290,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":298,"left":297,"right":24,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":297,"left":296,"right":23,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":296,"left":294,"right":295,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":294,"left":18,"right":293,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":293,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":295,"left":21,"right":22,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":303,"left":302,"right":29,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":302,"left":300,"right":301,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":300,"left":25,"right":26,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":301,"left":27,"right":28,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":328,"left":325,"right":327,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":325,"left":316,"right":324,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":316,"left":307,"right":315,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":307,"left":30,"right":306,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":306,"left":31,"right":32,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"